parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering system can cause the vehicle to veer off course, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel feels unstable
the vehicle wanders or drifts on the road
the steering wheel requires constant correction
the vehicle is difficult to control on imperfect road surfaces
the steering wheel housing separates or comes off track.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can prevent the airbag from deploying in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light activates
the passenger side airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident
the airbag system may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the passenger side airbag sensor can cause the airbag to shut off, increasing the risk of serious injury or fatality in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light activates
the passenger side airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident
the airbag system may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag System Design or Installation Flaw
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A design or installation flaw in the airbag system can cause the airbag to malfunction or not deploy in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of serious injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light activates
the passenger side airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident
the airbag system may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The hesitation and acceleration issues with the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded in traffic. This can be particularly dangerous when merging onto a freeway or driving on an expressway.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to accelerate when pressing the gas pedal
the transmission jerks or jumps when shifting
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the vehicle accelerates suddenly without warning
dashboard warning lights illuminate.
